{
  "stem": "22944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't the sort of method that they use today-- [INAUDIBLE] and Montessori and all modern ideas to occupy children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I do remember going, but I don't think I felt very happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About three hours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My eldest sister used to take me, or any of my other sisters, and spent a few hours there playing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't got very strong memories and happy recollection of my kindergarten period.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had plenty to do at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are one of six children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't work out, though, and it wasn't so much a custom in those days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had to run a home and look after her family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think that's plenty to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, things become disrupted after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things were not straightforward, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, things were politically changing, and I did not know as a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But things were changing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, obviously, moved to different area from Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in another district, we had to move out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went from that lovely flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We moved to another area called Judenstrasse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was another sort of small place we lived in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was within Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think the schooling was disrupted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't got tremendous lot of memories of that stage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From [INAUDIBLE] to-- I probably-- I must have been about four or five.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, because we stayed there 1940, '41 in Bratislava before we moved to Nitra.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I reckon I was about six-- six, seven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't have recollection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have got only impressions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think it was-- [? about ?] discussed with us the situation.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
